Sun May 10 10:00:05 UTC 2026 - Dirk Müller <dmueller@suse.com>

- update to 39.1.0:
  * (i18n) Expanded Turkish keywords
  * [Ruby, Python, JavaScript, Perl, C++, .NET] Optimise parser
    class/speed by removing redundant null `#detach` method
    (#561).
  * [c] Fixed memory leak with respect to the pickle ast ids.
  * [c] Fixed potential read past null terminator. Fixed
    allocation of more memory than necessary (#559).
  * [PHP] Fix PHP 8.4 deprecation warnings (#550).
  * [cpp] Added missing include guard in parser.hpp
  * [cpp] Removed unreachable code in parser.hpp
  * [Python] Drop support for python 3.9.

